2001-09-04	Olivier Poncet <ponceto@noos.fr>

	* Complete rewrite of the emulator. Needs the Athena (Xaw) widget set,
	  and/or a Motif 1.2 (Xm) compliant distribution to compile Xcpc (like
	  OpenMotif, Lesstif, OSF Motif, ...).

